attributes.name: accept
attributes.description: File types that can be accepted. See [input accept Attribute](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/file#accept)

attributes.name: beforeUpload
attributes.description: Hook function which will be executed before uploading. Uploading will be stopped with `false` or a rejected Promise returned.

attributes.name: customRequest
attributes.description: override for the default xhr behavior allowing for additional customization and ability to implement your own XMLHttpRequest

attributes.name: data
attributes.description: Uploading params or function which can return uploading params.

attributes.name: fileList
attributes.description: List of files that have been uploaded (controlled). Here is a common issue [#2423](https://github.com/ant-design/ant-design/issues/2423) when using it

attributes.name: headers
attributes.description: Set request headers, valid above IE10.

value.type: v-slot:itemRender="{originNode: VNode, file: UploadFile, fileList: object[], actions: { download: function, preview: function, remove: function }"

attributes.name: listType
attributes.description: Built-in stylesheets, support for three types: `text`, `picture` or `picture-card`

attributes.name: maxCount
attributes.description: Limit the number of uploaded files. Will replace current one when `maxCount` is `1`

attributes.name: multiple
attributes.description: Whether to support selected multiple file. `IE10+` supported. You can select multiple files with CTRL holding down while multiple is set to be true

attributes.name: showUploadList
attributes.description: Whether to show default upload list, could be an object to specify `showPreviewIcon`, `showRemoveIcon` and `showDownloadIcon` individually

value.type: boolean | { showPreviewIcon?: boolean, showRemoveIcon?: boolean, showDownloadIcon?: boolean }

attributes.name: supportServerRender
attributes.description: Need to be turned on while the server side is rendering.

attributes.name: status
attributes.description: Upload status. Show different style when configured

attributes.name: uid
attributes.description: unique id. Will auto generate when not provided
